    </div>

    <div class="title">
        <p>
            Select an action from the list above to view the relevant perspective.
        </p>
        <p>
            Examine your own perspectives from the options below.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div id="instructions" class="infoPanel">
        <a href="tateVideoInstructions.html" target="_blank"><img src="images/info.png"></a>
    </div>

